{"words":[{"word":"soliskin","count":5},{"word":"te","count":4},{"word":"rite","count":4},{"word":"must","count":3},{"word":"void","count":3},{"word":"time","count":3},{"word":"feast","count":3},{"word":"return","count":3},{"word":"friends","count":3},{"word":"people","count":2},{"word":"brings","count":2},{"word":"trust","count":2},{"word":"earned","count":2},{"word":"ask","count":2},{"word":"storm","count":2},{"word":"camp","count":2},{"word":"shepherdess","count":2},{"word":"saved","count":2},{"word":"yet","count":2},{"word":"great","count":2},{"word":"earlier","count":2},{"word":"tomorrow's","count":2},{"word":"href","count":2},{"word":"join","count":2},{"word":"body","count":2},{"word":"exostrider","count":2},{"word":"light","count":2},{"word":"new","count":2},{"word":"drink","count":2},{"word":"woods","count":2},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"halt","count":1},{"word":"clothing","count":1},{"word":"haldarheim","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"heh","count":1},{"word":"interesting","count":1},{"word":"feel","count":1},{"word":"safe","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"guiding","count":1},{"word":"sense","count":1},{"word":"carries","count":1},{"word":"aura","count":1},{"word":"spacetrek","count":1},{"word":"collective","count":1},{"word":"vast","count":1},{"word":"world","count":1},{"word":"beyond","count":1},{"word":"frostlands","count":1},{"word":"guise","count":1},{"word":"shepherds","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"grateful","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"near","count":1},{"word":"atuja","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"named","count":1},{"word":"astrid","count":1},{"word":"abides","count":1},{"word":"stray","count":1},{"word":"entrust","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"meaning","count":1},{"word":"known","count":1},{"word":"astrid's","count":1},{"word":"daughter","count":1},{"word":"stir","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"tangled","count":1},{"word":"weave","count":1},{"word":"lengths","count":1},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"academy's","count":1},{"word":"willingness","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"unexpected","count":1},{"word":"forgive","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"helped","count":1},{"word":"title","count":1},{"word":"shepherd","count":1},{"word":"tonight","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"gesture","count":1},{"word":"amends","count":1},{"word":"rudeness","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"forth","count":1},{"word":"roya","count":1},{"word":"call","count":1},{"word":"rest","count":1},{"word":"wish","count":1},{"word":"begin","count":1},{"word":"eighth","count":1},{"word":"hour","count":1},{"word":"night","count":1},{"word":"tomorrow","count":1},{"word":"marks","count":1},{"word":"send","count":1},{"word":"beloved","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"radiant","count":1},{"word":"transform","count":1},{"word":"sacred","count":1},{"word":"form","count":1},{"word":"farewell","count":1},{"word":"beginning","count":1},{"word":"wakes","count":1},{"word":"reunite","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"aside","count":1},{"word":"sorrow","count":1},{"word":"parting","count":1},{"word":"embrace","count":1},{"word":"joy","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"food","count":1},{"word":"heed","count":1},{"word":"fool","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"storm's","count":1},{"word":"fury","count":1},{"word":"upon","count":1},{"word":"enter","count":1},{"word":"bjartr","count":1},{"word":"disaster","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"centuries","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"believed","count":1},{"word":"solistrees'","count":1},{"word":"protects","count":1},{"word":"storms","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"times","count":1},{"word":"urge","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"safety","count":1},{"word":"quickly","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"You two. Please halt.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"From your clothing, I see of my people you are not. What brings you to Haldarheim?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Oh? A Soliskin...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Heh. How interesting... Soliskin trust only those they feel safe with. Its trust you have earned. My thanks for guiding it back.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"But I must ask, I sense one of you carries the aura of the Spacetrek Collective. The other, from the vast world beyond the frostlands. Why come under the guise of Shepherds?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Void Storm? You mean, the one just before?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Haha! Then grateful I must be to you both!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"But ask I must—the Void Storm, it happened near Atuja camp, yes?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"A Shepherdess named Astrid abides there. Saved the stray Soliskin you did, yet entrust it to a true Shepherdess you did not. Why come all this way?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Your meaning?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I should have known Astrid's daughter would stir such trouble! A tangled weave this time, but she will go to great lengths for her girl.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"The Academy's willingness to come this far is unexpected. Forgive my earlier words. You saved the Soliskin and helped our people. The title of \"Shepherd,\" you have earned.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Tonight, we hold a feast for tomorrow's <te href=700028>Rite of Return</te>. Join us, as a gesture to make amends for my earlier rudeness.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Come. From this day forth, the Roya call you friends.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Rest at the camp if you wish. The feast will begin at the eighth hour of the night.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Friends—it is time we feast!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Tomorrow marks the Rite of Return, where we send our beloved Soliskin back to the great body of the Exostrider. Into radiant light they will transform to join its sacred form.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Farewell it will be, yet a new beginning as well! For when the Exostrider wakes, we will reunite in its body!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Now, let us put aside the sorrow of parting and embrace the joy of new life with good food and drink!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"But heed this, my friends. Too much drink you will not have. Should you make a fool of yourself in tomorrow's Rite, help I will not give.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"What is it that brings you here? With the Void Storm's fury upon us, it is no time to enter Bjartr Woods.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"This is a disaster not seen in centuries. We have always believed the <te href=700027>Solistrees'</te> light protects the woods from such storms.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"The Rite of Return cannot be done, not in these times. I urge you both to head to safety, quickly!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002}]}